profile:
From sales to after-sales service, including manufacturing and installation, Portes et Fenetres BG employs thirty employees. Our doors and windows are manufactured exclusively at our factory by our professionals and specialized technicians. The company also has its own teams of installers to guarantee you the best service and avoid the inconvenience of dealing with subcontractors.

Our young, dynamic and motivated team continue to deliver quality product year after year with unmatched customer satisfaction. Come and meet us and you will be pleasantly surprised with our service, quality, price and speed of delivery.
